Subject: 8 Conlay at Kuala Lumpur
Description:
1. The above pricing does not includes installation changes and optional item such as gate valve, thermometer, check valve 
2. Heater comes with 1.5 meter length of 2.5mm 3 core flexible cable.
3. Heater does not come with plug top as it is the new regulation from Suruhanjaya Tenaga. 
4. Ensure all the check valve / gate valve at the incoming and out going pipes at the heater are shut off during your 
    pressure test on your piping. Do not supply water into the heater and do not do a pressure test on the heater. 
5. The heater should only be fed with municipal water which comply to National Drinking Water Quality Standards (NDWQS) for
    Testing & Commissioning before Vacant Possession (VP).   
6. Operating Pressure should not exceed 6 bars.
7. Pipes connection and fittings torque < 60Nm.
8. Ensure all electrical components and wiring are secured firmly.  Apply a pull test of 5Nm. Electrical connections must be 
     made by qualified electrician in compliance with local or international electrical commission regulations.
9. Ensure the heater installed within a dedicated service space with a minimum clearance of 600mm on all sides.
10. All heaters comes with Film Wrap. Additional cost for Bubble Wrap or Carton Box.
